GET books.You can play around with CRUD operations for books

• GET /books — list all books

• GET /books/1 — retrieve one book

• POST /books — create a book

• PUT /books/1 — replace a book

• PATCH /books/1 — update selected fields

• DELETE /books/1 — delete a book
